    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="Install_LAMP_+_Wordpress">Install LAMP + Wordpress</h2><p>###Step One - Install Apache<br>    sudo apt-get update  (update ubuntu package list)<br>    sudo apt-get install apache2</p>
<p>###Step Two - Install Mysql<br><code># 不是必要的指令</code> </p>
<pre><code>sudo apt-<span class="keyword">get</span> install mysql-server php5-mysql
sudo mysql_install_db ( create <span class="keyword">it</span>'s database directory structure) <span class="comment">#</span>
sudo mysql_secure_installation (<span class="command">run</span> a simple security <span class="keyword">script</span>) <span class="comment">#</span>
</code></pre><h3 id="Step_Three_—_Install_PHP">Step Three — Install PHP</h3><pre><code>sudo apt-<span class="keyword">get</span> install php5 libapache2-<span class="keyword">mod</span>-php5 php5-mcrypt
</code></pre><h2 id="Install_WordPress_on_Ubuntu_Apache">Install WordPress on Ubuntu Apache</h2><p>###Step One - Install unzip (for digitalOcean)<br><code>Linode 已自動安裝</code></p>
<pre><code>sudo apt-<span class="keyword">get</span> install unzip
</code></pre><p>###Step Two - Install WordPress SoftWare<br>    cd /var/www <return><br>    wget <a href="https://tw.wordpress.org/latest-zh_TW.zip" target="_blank" rel="external">https://tw.wordpress.org/latest-zh_TW.zip</a> <return></return></return></p>
<p>###Step Three - 修改 wordpress 資料夾名稱<br><code>更改為test.tw</code></p>
<pre><code>mv wordpress <span class="keyword">test</span>.<span class="keyword">tw</span> &lt;<span class="keyword">return</span>&gt;
<span class="keyword">cd</span> <span class="keyword">test</span>.<span class="keyword">tw</span> &lt;<span class="keyword">return</span>&gt;
<span class="keyword">mkdir</span> logs &lt;retrn&gt; (新增logs資料夾)
<span class="keyword">cd</span> .. &lt;<span class="keyword">return</span>&gt;
</code></pre><h3 id="Step_Four_-_設定wordpress_目錄權限">Step Four - 設定wordpress 目錄權限</h3><pre><code>chown -R www-<span class="type">data</span>:www-<span class="type">data</span> test.tw &lt;<span class="keyword">return</span>&gt;
</code></pre><h3 id="Step_five_-_設定固定網址參數">Step five - 設定固定網址參數</h3><pre><code>sudo a2enmod rewrite &lt;<span class="keyword">return</span>&gt;
<span class="keyword">cd</span> <span class="keyword">test</span>.<span class="keyword">tw</span> &lt;<span class="keyword">return</span>&gt;
touch .htaccess &lt;<span class="keyword">return</span>&gt;
chmod 777 .htaccess &lt;<span class="keyword">return</span>&gt;
</code></pre><p><code>**在Wordpress固定網址頁面更新您要的固定網址結構</code><br><br><code>再將「.htaccess」檔案存取權限變更為644</code></p>
<pre><code>chmod <span class="number">644</span> .htaccess &lt;<span class="keyword">return</span>&gt;
</code></pre><h3 id="Step_Seven_-_新增wordpress_db">Step Seven - 新增wordpress db</h3><pre><code>sudo mysql -uroot -pscum0923 &lt;<span class="keyword">return</span>&gt;
</code></pre><p><code>mysql &gt;</code></p>
<pre><code>create database <span class="built_in">test</span>; &lt;<span class="built_in">return</span>&gt;
<span class="built_in">exit</span> &lt;<span class="built_in">return</span>&gt;
</code></pre><p>##Install Ubuntu Virtual Host</p>
<p>###Step One - 新增 Virtual Host<br>    cd / <return><br>    cd /etc/apache2/sites-available <return><br>    nano test.tw.conf <return></return></return></return></p>
<p><code>test.tw.conf 內容</code> <code>ctrl + o --&gt;save</code> <code>ctrl + x --&gt;exit</code></p>
<pre><code>&lt;VirtualHost *:80&gt;
    ServerAdmin nono520@gmail.com
    DocumentRoot /<span class="keyword">var</span>/www/<span class="keyword">test</span>.<span class="keyword">tw</span>/
    ServerName <span class="keyword">test</span>.<span class="keyword">tw</span>
    ServerAlias www.<span class="keyword">test</span>.<span class="keyword">tw</span>
    ErrorLog /<span class="keyword">var</span>/www/<span class="keyword">test</span>.<span class="keyword">tw</span>/logs/<span class="keyword">error</span>.<span class="literal">log</span>
    CustomLog /<span class="keyword">var</span>/www/<span class="keyword">test</span>.<span class="keyword">tw</span>/logs/access.<span class="keyword">log</span> combined
    &lt;Directory /<span class="keyword">var</span>/www/<span class="keyword">test</span>.<span class="keyword">tw</span>/&gt;
            Options Indexes FollowSymLinks MultiViews
            AllowOverride All
            <span class="keyword">Order</span> allow,deny
            allow from all
     &lt;/Directory&gt;
&lt;/VirtualHost&gt;
</code></pre><p>###Step Two - 使 test.tw 生效<br>    sudo a2ensite test.tw.conf <retrun><br>    sudo service apache2 restart <return></return></retrun></p>
<p>##Over </p>
<p>###打開Brower<br>    <a href="http://test.tw" target="_blank" rel="external">http://test.tw</a> <return> </return></p>
]]></content>
